title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table which is inside a grid cell.
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Data in the table inside the grid cell should be exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a table into one grid cell. 
2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the tables inside the grid cells.
